    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape! It drives super smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's totally ready for all your upcoming adventures. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it feels. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of this beauty!",
