    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 inline-six. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains rigid with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension retains its precise geometry with recently refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows the honest patina of a driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain is robust, exhibiting no signs of rod bearing failure or VANOS rattle. This is a true analog machine for the discerning pilot looking for a spirited daily or a solid weekend platform.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
