    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 Lexus RX 350 in Eminent White Pearl. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and remains in impressive overall shape. The exterior paint retains a deep gloss, with only a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014nothing that detracts from its elegant curb appeal. Inside, the Parchment leather upholstery is clean and free of tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All premium features, including the heated/ventilated seats, navigation system, and power liftgate, are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has a complete service history with recent oil changes, a fresh cabin air filter, and brake pads that were replaced within the last 5,000 miles. The tires provide excellent grip with significant tread depth remaining. It delivers a whisper-quiet ride and smooth acceleration, representing a fantastic opportunity for someone seeking luxury without the new-car price tag. Includes two key fobs and all original owner manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
