      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go! It\u2019s got a few tiny signs of love here and there, but overall it looks great and drives even better. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
