    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example benefits from a documented VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, essential for maintaining chassis rigidity and timing precision. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring excellent traction during lateral acceleration. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping characteristics with updated bushings for precise turn-in. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains in peak operating condition, offering the visceral, naturally aspirated performance these chassis are renowned for.",
